{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860293493,"sessionID":"ses_2867b25baffebIQ2bO39tU5xmp","part":{"id":"prt_d79859abd00119c6p1tDk75zuA","messageID":"msg_d79858879001B5T0d2AIYqosf1","sessionID":"ses_2867b25baffebIQ2bO39tU5xmp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 Tasks: CRD Shared Types and Constants\n2: \n3: > **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n4: > **Language:** Go  \n5: > **Size:** S  \n6: > **Stage:** ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Task 1: Create common_types.go\n11: **Verifiable Output:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/common_types.go` exists with shared type definitions\n12: \n13: - [ ] Create `common_types.go` file in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n14: - [ ] Define `RuntimePhase` enum type with values: Pending, Running, Succeeded, Failed, Unknown\n15: - [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=Pending;Running;Succeeded;Failed;Unknown` marker\n16: - [ ] Define `Condition` struct with fields: Type, Status, Reason, Message, LastTransitionTime\n17: - [ ] Define `ConditionType` string type\n18: - [ ] Define `ConditionStatus` string type with constants: ConditionTrue, ConditionFalse, ConditionUnknown\n19: - [ ] Define `SecretKeySelector` struct with fields: LocalObjectReference, Key\n20: - [ ] Define `ConfigMapKeySelector` struct with fields: LocalObjectReference, Key\n21: - [ ] Define `LocalObjectReference` struct with field: Name\n22: - [ ] Add JSON tags using camelCase naming for all fields\n23: - [ ] Add proper documentation comments for all types\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ## Task 2: Create constants.go\n28: **Verifiable Output:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go` exists with API constants\n29: \n30: - [ ] Create `constants.go` file in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n31: - [ ] Define `GroupName` constant with value \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n32: - [ ] Define `Version` constant with value \"v1alpha1\"\n33: - [ ] Define condition type constants: Ready, Available, Progressing\n34: - [ ] Define event reason constants: Created, Updated, Deleted, Failed, Succeeded\n35: - [ ] Add proper documentation comments for all constants\n36: - [ ] Ensure constants follow Go naming conventions (PascalCase for exported)\n37: \n38: ---\n39: \n40: ## Task 3: Add Kubebuilder Markers to Shared Types\n41: **Verifiable Output:** All shared types have appropriate kubebuilder markers\n42: \n43: - [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:object:root=false` marker for non-root types\n44: - [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:validation:Required` for required fields\n45: - [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:validation:Optional` for optional fields\n46: - [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:validation:Pattern` where applicable\n47: - [ ] Ensure markers follow Kubernetes API conventions\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Task 4: Update register.go with Shared Types\n52: **Verifiable Output:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` properly references shared types\n53: \n54: - [ ] Verify GroupName constant is used in register.go\n55: - [ ] Ensure shared types are implicitly registered via CRD types\n56: - [ ] Verify SchemeBuilder includes all necessary types\n57: - [ ] Confirm AddToScheme function works with shared types\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## Task 5: Generate DeepCopy Methods for Shared Types\n62: **Verifiable Output:** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` contains DeepCopy methods for shared types\n63: \n64: - [ ] Run `controller-gen object:headerFile=\"hack/boilerplate.go.txt\" paths=\"./...\"`\n65: - [ ] Verify `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy`, `DeepCopyObject` methods generated for `Condition`\n66: - [ ] Verify DeepCopy methods generated for `SecretKeySelector`\n67: - [ ] Verify DeepCopy methods generated for `ConfigMapKeySele